successes.title: The Nomad CNC Mill
successes.description: The Nomad 883 is a ready-to-run CNC Mill that's at home in any environment.

Pledges.description: HIGH FIVE!  - Our most sincere thanks and a Carbide 3D sticker.
THE EARLIEST BIRD - Get in early and receive a Nomad 883 with material and cutter STARTER PACK before anyone else.
INVENTOR - Get a machine in the second production run with the material and cutter STARTER PACK.
MAKER - Get a machine in the third production run with the material and cutter STARTER PACK.

Builder - Get a machine in the fourth production run with the material and cutter STARTER PACK.
Begins shipping after the MAKER level production run.

CARBIDE INNER CIRCLE - At this pledge level you will get a Nomad 883 with the material and cutter MEGA PACK, a jig for two-sided machining, and a free upgrade to MeshCAM Pro. Nomads at this level will ship after the early bird rewards.
CARBIDE INNER CIRCLE (Batch 2) - At this pledge level you will get a Nomad 883 with the material and cutter MEGA PACK, the jig for two-sided machining, and a free upgrade to MeshCAM Pro.

CARBIDE INNER CIRCLE (Batch 3) - At this pledge level you will get a Nomad 883 with the material and cutter MEGA PACK, a jig for two-sided machining, and a free upgrade to MeshCAM Pro. Nomads at this level will begin shipping in December.

CARBIDE INNER CIRCLE (Batch 4) - At this pledge level you will get a Nomad 883 with the material and cutter MEGA PACK, a jig for two-sided machining, and a free upgrade to MeshCAM Pro.  We expect Nomads at this level to begin shipping in Jan, after batch #3.
